</span></h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-15_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Ensuring the security of sensitive information in the early years<br><br></em>In today’s digital age, data protection and confidentiality are of paramount importance, especially in early years settings where sensitive information about children, families, and staff is collected and stored. A comprehensive data protection and confidentiality policy ensures that early years providers comply with legal obligations and protect personal data from misuse or unauthorised access. 
